            <url>https://shebanq.ancient-data.org/</url><CLARINCentre>DANS</CLARINCentre><OriginalSource>https://github.com/ETCBC/shebanq/blob/master/docs/cmdi/SHEBANQ.cmdi.xml</OriginalSource>
